## Frequently asked questions

Get the answers you need right away.

###  _expand_more_ Why should you work with Web.com?

Web.com is a leading web technology company and one of the nation’s largest
providers of website builder and online marketing services. Since 1999, we’ve
served more than 3 million customers around the world, and we manage over 9
million domain names. We offer a variety of comprehensive solutions with all
the tools small businesses need to succeed online, and all our services are
backed by an award-winning customer support team.

###  _expand_more_ Why do I need a website for my business?

A website helps you promote your business online and establish credibility
with your customers. For customers to find you online, it’s important to have
a professional website that offers helpful, relevant content and provides a
good experience for users. Whether you want to build an online store, launch
an online blog, or create an affiliate marketing website, Web.com has you
covered.

###  _expand_more_ Should I use a website builder or hire a website designer?

We offer both options. If you need a website quickly, then we have an easy-to-
use website builder with over a hundred website templates to choose from. Once
you find a template you love, you can customize it to fit your needs and get
online fast.  
  
If you’re short on time, then let our website design experts create a custom
website that checks all the boxes. You’ll get a professional design with fresh
content written for your customers and search engines in mind.

###  _expand_more_ What is a domain name and why do I need one?

A domain name is the URL of your website. Think of it as the address for your
customers to find your website online. A branded, keyword-rich domain name is
a great way to give your business a more professional presence online, build
credibility, increase brand awareness and improve your search engine rankings.

###  _expand_more_ Why do businesses use Web.com for their digital marketing?

We provide a full range of digital marketing services for every type and size
of business and budget, with campaigns designed for both local and global
markets. Our Pay-Per-Click (PPC) agents are specially trained to assist you
with Google advertising, a service which allows you to choose specific
keywords and appear in ads at the top of search pages. We also offer search
engine optimization (SEO) services to determine the right keywords and content
strategy for raising your search ranking. If you’d like to connect with more
people on social media, we’ll help you grow your audience in the places your
customers spend time online.

###  _expand_more_ How can I keep my website secure online?

You can keep your website secure and your customers’ information safe with an
SSL certificate. An SSL certificate will validate your identity online and
encrypt private information, such as payment and customer account information.
A secure website will gain your customers’ trust and improve your search
engine performance.

###  _expand_more_ How does Web.com help small businesses?

With more than two decades in business, we put our experience to work for you.
Our customer service experts provide unlimited support when you need it, and
we offer a wide range of resources to help you succeed online. When you’re
ready to create a professional website, we’ll match you with a website builder
coach who makes it easier to get your site up and running. If you ever have
any questions or need assistance along the way, we’ll be here to help every
step of the way.
